data.description: Out in the country but less than 10 minutes to downtown Vidalia! This home features one story living with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths in the main house as well as an open kitchen/dining area and 2 car garage. The master bath has just been completely renovated and features a beautiful double vanity with marble top, a freestanding soaking tub, and separate walk-in tiled shower. A large closet and private toilet room will make this space one of your favorite places to escape! There is new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the living area, new paint, newer roof and HVAC.  A separate detached garage/workshop features an apartment above with separate entrance. A partial wrap around porch adds southern charm and is a perfect spot for rocking and sweet tea sipping! An above ground pool with large deck will offer much relief from these hot summer days we've been having. Lastly, a fenced in yard provides a secure spot for pets or play! Call today for an appt to view!
